# Reflection

## What I Learned

A research summary can contain accurate information while still being incomplete. Identifying what has been omitted is just as important as identifying factual errors. Comprehensive research should address the full scope of the question, acknowledge limitations, and consider multiple perspectives.

---

## What I'd Do Differently

Compare the AI-generated summary against systematic reviews or clinical guidelines to identify additional research gaps and ensure that important evidence has not been overlooked.

